{"tid":2460841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"列堤頓道強檢大廈 醫生世家廿二歲困昏迷不治","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:49:14.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"604a0844c4d2c5c103aae637ec35ef7a7ac7e5b6","tid":2460841,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210325/S3CA57JZTZCILJK7CU5ND7Y7WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210325%2FS3CA57JZTZCILJK7CU5ND7Y7WA%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxlLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=506235bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210325%2FS3CA57JZTZCILJK7CU5ND7Y7WA%2F&h=9f85aa50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210325/S3CA57JZTZCILJK7CU5ND7Y7WA/</a>"},{"pid":"786b8fb809a86fb4a78705106a400a505bc023d6","tid":2460841,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"因為有確診者而須強檢的中區列堤頓道52號嘉和苑，今晨9時半，一名姓王22歲青年，被母發現昏迷不醒，報警求助。救護員到場經檢驗，證實男事主已告不治。警方列有人昏迷，兩名穿着全套白色保護衣的警員登樓調查。據了解，事主有病歷記錄，惟死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，事主的父母均是醫生，自細體弱多病，警員調查後撿走一批藥物，當中包括有甲狀腺藥。<br />\n<br />\nURSUS Fitness健身室爆疫，由於不少顧客均居於港島，以致港島中半山不少大廈被列入強制檢測名單。本月13日半山區15幢大廈的居民因此要強檢，包括今次有人猝死的嘉和苑。"},{"pid":"b8fcd78ed7815cb96b7545003da164211331013b","tid":2460841,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"d新聞講到好似強檢期間死人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}